OL,4,CBurglar and victims become friends
OL,5,Cthrough rehabilitation scheme
OL,6, A burglary victim has become "best of
OL,7, friends" with the man who broke into
OL,8, her home.
OL,10,FThe 41-year-old stole #500 along with
OL,11,Felectrical items from Anne and Terry
OL,12,FLinton's house in Erdington,
OL,13,FBirmingham, in May 2019.
OL,15,FThe thief was caught, but instead of
OL,16,Fbeing sent to jail was placed on a
OL,17,Frehabilitation programme and now looks
OL,18,Fafter their garden.
OL,20,FMrs Linton said: "Even a fairytale
OL,21,Fstory could not end like this."
